Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:40.10,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.68,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:51.42,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:57.73,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:04.08,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:07.37,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.50,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats reach the New World at long last,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the harshest sea, ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,After receiving an emergency signal,\Nthey landed on Punk Hazard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,a strange island divided into two parts—\Nthe Burning Lands and the Frozen Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sink to your death, Devil Fruit users!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap. Let us look inside the {research }institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If Straw Hat comes, I'll chop his head off for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's all you have to say, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats?! Children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I got out of the building! I can go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering who this villainous guy was! Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not good! The Navy's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't escape from here! Let's look for another exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What brought the Navy to such a place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, kids! Go to the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a backdoor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, let's catch the Straw Hats!
