Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Brownbeard-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Brownbeard-sama! Sama... Sama... Sama... Sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never heard of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How can they be so ignorant?!
