Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yes! He did it! --That's our Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The boat capsized!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?! Struggle as much as you like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'll be swallowed by the water!
