Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry up... O-Or I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't take long!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, what happened, Roro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are sharks in a lake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's technically a sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight between Red Hound and Blue Pheasant left a crater just like after an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And then seawater streamed in from a big crack and created a lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, so did a lot of sea life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharks! Scary! Sharks! Zoro got bitten by a shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim carefully! There is nothing they can do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no place to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Blow them to kingdom come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I've never thought my life would end like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is colder than a freezing blizzard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the wind from the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did I mention I froze your gun barrels?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So they'll explode if you shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you, skull mask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is not worth mentioning. It's Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You just mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a skeleton who came back from the dead and put my second life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the hands of the Straw Hat captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,People call me Soul King!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When did he freeze our guns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Unforgivable"? Right back at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--You bastard! --How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing friends - I'm sick of it (korigori)! {TL Note}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And it sounds like ice (koori)! {TL Note}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fast! He sure can fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know they had another crewmember!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't matter now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they already became shark food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The sharks got their butts kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just in time, Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was chased by a strange thing and happened to come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice try, you part-human-part-animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But sharks can't stop us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're way stronger than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter... how strong we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't stand the cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing! I'm gonna turn to ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.53,"Sign",,0,0,12,,{\an2}"I told you guys..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:32.00,"Sign",,0,0,12,,{\an2}"We can't just go to the cold side like this..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But look. We're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be glad that we ran into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, they're right on top of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! They look familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the fourth guy from the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the guy next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl at the far left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs70\bord4\pos(17,1024)}Their clothes look warm!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.40,0:13:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\bord4\pos(966.6,1024)}Their clothes look warm!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:14.40,0:13:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs70\bord4\pos(1910,1024)}Their clothes look warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:21.22,"Sign",,0,0,12,,{\an2}"All right... please get me one, too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they looking to rip our coats off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're terrible! Do they wanna rob us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! That hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the rookie of that worst generation from two years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He is Fire Fist's brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A pirate with a 400-million-berry bounty - Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,4... 400 million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mil Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't have to hurt you so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my friends. You're in better shape than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:08.32,Sign,,0,0,266,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\fs66\bord2.33\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}Research Institute, {in front of the }Main Entrance
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.82,0:15:08.32,Sign,,0,0,266,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\fs66\bord0\4a&HFF&}Research Institute, {in front of the }Main Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, Smo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I said I didn't want anything to do with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Hi-ya! It's this way, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta find a backdoor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back! It was that man who cut me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he may have the rest of your body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, it can wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! Maybe I can get a clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to find a backdoor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go back to face the Navy again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any exit! Where is the backdoor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Super count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You got some kind of sensor on you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you take the lead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That was that samurai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...And the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:16:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?! It's like a thin film...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? I felt something weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No time to think about it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, keep running, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Did I drop my cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.72,0:17:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is no time for you to fool around, Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In this week's episode, I'm super!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find a backdoor in a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,--Everybody? --There's something wrong with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, my breasts feel lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,These are...! I got big breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I turned into a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When did it happen? I'm a raccoon dog now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Everybody, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do a roll call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,--Chopper! --Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--Franky! --Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Nami... aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Law, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us back our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't have it as it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's falling toward us! --Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's retreat for now, Vice Admiral! His power is too creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been fused to the rocks of the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He made some sort of strange artwork with the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! We can't make it back to the base without the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Warlords work for the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're breaking your contract by attacking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Trafalgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,--We'll report this to headquarters! --They'll strip you of your title!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Scan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Transponder Snails?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Mine's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No way... So is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He took all of our Transponder Snails!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you tell the headquarters or the Government
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,about anything that you've seen on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid pirate, don't push your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You ate the Op-Op Fruit and you're the modification man, I believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of his sword's reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I got cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are in my way! Get out of the circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The circle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,While you're in the circle he created,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you're like a patient on an operating table!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is his operating room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He has total control over it and can manipulate anything as he pleases!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the Surgeon of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Trafalgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really wanna do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Haki is not strong enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.13,0:22:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,With Tashigi being cut down,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the thugs of the Navy's G-5 unit were also about to face annihilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But then Smoker faces Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A duel between a Warlord and a Navy Vice Admiral finally begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.63,0:23:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Their fierce battle that destroys everything around them
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly takes an unexpected turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Clash!\NLaw vs. Vice Admiral Smoker"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
