Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.99,0:23:35.00,Title Card - Top,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.3\4a&HFF&}A Clash!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:35.00,Title Card - Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.3\c&H000000&}Law vs. Vice Admiral Smoker
